-- Fortress’s Novogratz Says U.S. Stocks May Increase 30%
-- B y   K a t h e r i n e   B u r t o n
-- 2013-05-08T14:49:03Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2013-05-08/fortress-s-novogratz-says-u-s-stocks-may-increase-30-.html
Michael Novogratz, head of liquid
markets at Fortress Investment Group LLC, says that U.S. stocks
could end the year up 25 percent to 30 percent.  “There is nothing on the horizon that gets me scared,” he
said in an interview today with  Erik Schatzker  on Bloomberg
Television.  To contact the reporter on this story:
